/ Thisparticularworkbelongstoaserieswhichwasinspiredbyscenesfrommoviesandadvertisementsinpopularmagazines/ ./ Withitsunusualpositioningofthefigure/ ,/ theartistwasinspiredwhileshewasworkingonaparticularexhibitionwith/ '/ AliceinWonderland/ '/ astheunderlyingtheme/ ./ Bysubvertingthenorm/ ,/ Geraldinequestionsiflifemimicsartorviceversa/ ./ 
