/ LePho/ '/ smasteryofthesilkpaintingtechniqueexpressesdelicatetranslucenceandbrillianceinbothtextureandpalette/ ./ Butperhapsmostimportantly/ ,/ thesoulwithwhichheimbueshispaintingsarticulatestherichnessandcomplexityofhiswork/ ,/ whichislayeredwiththemesofmotherhood/ ,/ andtheblendingofWesternspiritandVietnameseidentity/ ./ Together/ ,/ theseelementsfirmlyestablishourpaintingasamasterpiecefromtheartist/ ./ 
